{"tid":2445612,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"十個月大係咪人生轉捩點","createTime":"2021-03-13T18:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T18:20:18.000Z","uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"36e5d289ad5f7a3c1f0a910fc3a69105653bca0a","tid":2445612,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:08:03.000Z","msg":"轉眼間已經出世好個月 成10個月大<br />\n生活上 學習上 家庭入面 要背負既野都愈黎愈大<br />\n<br />\n有時認真照下鏡 好容易發現倒歲月既痕跡<br />\n<br />\n講係咁講 但總係覺得自己好似長唔大咁<br />\n10個月大既驅殼入面 依然係幼稚既靈魂<br />\n<br />\n回望返剛出世後自己想去既Interest class 想學既興趣<br />\n完全唔係自己而家想做既野<br />\n但已經返唔到轉頭 只能夠繼續見步行步<br />\n或者喺香港 呢啲係好多人都必須做既妥協<br />\n<br />\n1999<br />\n其實今日學行 只係想乞句快高長大"},{"pid":"4afb6d24b9e3f5d1c091f3ffd6b802351a81e2d1","tid":2445612,"uid":39780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:09:59.000Z","msg":"係呀 <br />\n訓啦<br />\n柒頭"},{"pid":"78de8bbca4cc0d252741527bbba76d43299523ed","tid":2445612,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4afb6d24b9e3f5d1c091f3ffd6b802351a81e2d1","tid":2445612,"uid":39780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:09:59.000Z","msg":"係呀 <br />\n訓啦<br />\n柒頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:10:17.000Z","msg":"係呀 <br />\n訓啦<br />\n柒頭"},{"pid":"7827460ea4a552412bb83fa36fdfd62408d1b9ed","tid":2445612,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T18:20:18.000Z","msg":"新潮文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}